&lt;p&gt;    @jeking3 thanks, good poinit. I&apos;ve checked the &lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;doc&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;a href=&quot;http://erlang.org/doc/programming_examples/bit_syntax.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://erlang.org/doc/programming_examples/bit_syntax.html&lt;/a&gt;) but couldn&apos;t find any `double`.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &amp;gt; The type can be integer, float, or binary.&lt;/p&gt;

